quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  109,1,"Sema: Enyi makafiri"
  109,2,Siabudu mnacho kiabudu
  109,3,Wala nyinyi hamuabudu ninaye muabudu
  109,4,Wala sitaabudu mnacho abudu
  109,5,Wala nyinyi hamuabudu ninaye muabudu
  109,6,"Nyinyi mna dini yenu, nami nina Dini yangu"
  110,1,Itakapo kuja nusura ya Mwenyezi Mungu na ushindi
  110,2,Na ukaona watu wanaingia katika Dini ya Mwenyezi Mungu kwa makundi
  110,3,"Zitakase sifa za Mola wako Mlezi, na umwombe msamaha; hakika Yeye ndiye anaye pokea toba"
  111,1,"Imeangamia mikono ya Abu Lahab, na yeye pia ameangamia"
  111,2,"Hayatamfaa mali yake, wala alivyo vichuma"
  111,3,Atauingia Moto wenye mwako
  111,4,"Na mkewe, mchukuzi wa kuni"
  111,5,Shingoni mwake iko kamba iliyo sokotwa